  "texts": [
    "The continuous response variable was discretised manually for each dataset, the original continuous labels and new class values for each dataset are shown in Fig. 3.",
    "Both Covid3Month and FloodModeling2 had a minimum label value with many cases.",
    "For both of these, this minimum label value has been converted into its own class label.",
    "For problems where there are no obvious places where the label can be separated into classes by value (including Covid3Month where the value is greater than 0), a split point was manually selected taking into account the average label value and the number of cases in each class for a splitting point.",
    "This leaves 11 datasets that are completely new to the archive."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}